{
  "stem": "1826.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No-- no normal human being could expect such systematic-- systematic annihilation of-- of-- of six million people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somebody could expect there'll be some-- some pogroms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some-- some-- you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was always a pessimist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I still couldn't expect anything like that, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nobody could expect anything like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But human beings are not human.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What's going on now in-- in Bosnia [INAUDIBLE] and I forget.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Kill each other like-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, let's hope that people get a little more humane.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Let's hope.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Thank God, I am glad that I live in a country, that I live-- that I live in America.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I came to this country as a worker for the Polish embassy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But after three, three and a half years, the situation in Poland became very-- under Stalin, very communistic, very totalitarian, very bad.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when they told me I had to go back, I-- I decided to stay here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never was any political person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I go-- I remember I came to New York because I had somebody who came already after the war.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went to-- to-- to a drug store and asked them, said I can type a letter with two fingers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I wrote the letter Dean Acheson, who was Secretary of State at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I wrote a letter, Honor-- Honorable Dean Acheson, Secretary of State, and I told him that I came here as a member of the Polish embassy, that now I am supposed to go back, but I asked for political asylum.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I added, I am not nor have I ever been a member of the Communist Party.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I became-- I became American citizen by the Act-- a special Act of the Congress.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
